q2_2:

1) "make"/ "make all" /"make client_server"
2) "./server"
3) Open new terminal-
4) "./client <server_pid> <signal> <amount_of_signals>"
5) In order to kill the server: " kill -9 <server_pid>

* The server pid is given while running the program (./server)
* The signal should be 2 or 10.

*The explenation about the siganls that were not caught is in the "q22_315242412.pdf" file.



